`,e.jsxs(o.p,{children:["One of the more common tools that is used across many agentic applications is the ability to search the web. With models being trained on specific sets of data, they tend to have a ",e.jsx(o.em,{children:"cutoff date"}),", which is when the information used to train the model was last updated."]}),`
