`,e.jsx(o.p,{children:"One of the larger value propositions that x402 brings to the table is the ability to have payments move at the speed of blockchains instead of traditional financial institutions. In reality, even Ethereum with ~12-minute finality is still faster than most traditional credit card payment settlement and ACH/cross-border processing times."}),`
