`,e.jsx(o.p,{children:"This means that while other networks would come to a standstill and see massive volatility and potential stability issues, SKALE would be able to handle the needed load to serve a significant portion of the onchain settlement of micropayments via x402 for agents on just a single SKALE Chain."}),`
